1.cognitive understanding. It’s your ability to understand the concept

2.emotional mastery. That’s where you have heard something with enough repetition, and it’s stimulated enough feelings inside you—desires, hungers, fears, concerns—that now you become conscious and capable of consistently using what you’ve learned

3.physical mastery. That means you don’t have to think about what you do; your actions are second nature. And the only way to get it is through consistent repetition.

